Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,STRAIGHT FROM THE HART, BECAUSE HVAC\NCLEANING SHOULD BE A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:08.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND, YOU KNOW, THAT HAS A COUPLE PLAYS TO\NIT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.75,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT SHOULD BE A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE, MEANING
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.88,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S THE METHOD THAT WE'RE GOING TO\NDISCUSS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.21,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IS POSITIVE AIR DUCT CLEANING, AS OPPOSED TO\NNEGATIVE AIR DUCT CLEANING.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:17.92,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND, YOU KNOW, IT SHOULD BE POSITIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.06,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT SHOULD BE A FUN THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.68,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT SHOULD BE A JOY FOR EVERYBODY DOING IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:30.36,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELCOME TO STRAIGHT FROM THE HART, BECAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:32.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HVAC CLEANING SHOULD BE A POSITIVE\NEXPERIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:36.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M YOUR HOST, DAVID BAKER, AND TODAY I'M\NJOINED
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:39.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BY RAMAIR INTERNATIONAL FOUNDER OF CEO DAVID\NHART.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:45.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IN THIS LAUNCH EPISODE, DAVID SHARES THE\NSTORY BEHIND POSITIVE AIR DUCT CLEANING.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE RAMAIR EQUIPMENT THAT'S TRANSFORMING\NBUSINESSES.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:52.15,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE REAL CUSTOMER WINS WE'LL BE\NFEATURING IN THE WEEKS AHEAD,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:55.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,INCLUDING OUR FIRST GUEST, BOB JORDAN OF\NPUROCLEAN NORTHWEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.91,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IF YOU'RE IN THE HVAC RESTORATION AND DUCT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:01:00.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,CLEANING INDUSTRY AND WANT PRACTICAL\NINSIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:04.01,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,TO ACTUALLY MOVE THE NEEDLE YOU'RE IN THE\NRIGHT PLACE, LET'S GET STRAIGHT TO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:05.82,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HERE'S DAVID HART.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DAVID, HOW ARE YOU DOING TODAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:08.82,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,GREAT, THANKS, DAVE. HOW'S IT GOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:10.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DOING WELL, DOING WELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S GOING ON THERE IN OREGON?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:13.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,A LOT OF DUCT CLEANING.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:14.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,GOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:20.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AS I THINK YOU PROBABLY KNOW, IN ADDITION TO\NRAMAIR, I ALSO HAVE AN HVAC CLEANING AND
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:23.05,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DE-CONTAMINATION COMPANY OUT HERE, AND WE\NARE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:28.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ABSOLUTELY SLAMMED WITH EVERYTHING FROM\NRESIDENTIAL TO COMMERCIAL TO RESTORATIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:29.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S TERRIFIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:30.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S TERRIFIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HEY, WE'RE LAUNCHING A NEW SHOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S STRAIGHT FROM THE HART.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,TALK ABOUT THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:39.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHY ARE WE DOING THIS AND WHAT'S OUR CONTENT\NGOING TO BE?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:44.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, I THINK THIS IS THE RIGHT TIME TO DO\NTHIS, DAVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:51.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DUCT CLEANING HAS BEEN AROUND FOR A LONG\NTIME SINCE THE 1950S, AND THE WAY IT'S
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:57.57,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BEEN DONE HAS BEEN WITH A TRADITIONAL METHOD\NTHAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:03.98,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WAS FINE FOR THE DAY BASED ON THE\NCONSTRUCTION OF DUCTING THAT WAS BEING CLEANED.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:08.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE CONSTRUCTION OF IT HAS EVOLVED, AND YET\NTHE METHODOLOGY HADN'T.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:12.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE EQUIPMENT, THE METHODOLOGY, ALL WAS THE\NSAME, AND IT WAS KIND OF STUCK IN THAT DEAL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:19.38,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,UNTIL ABOUT 18 YEARS AGO WHEN ANOTHER METHOD\NCAME UP, CAME ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:23.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE REASON I SAY, I THINK THIS IS THE\NRIGHT TIME NOW, RATHER THAN 18 OR 10 YEARS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.72,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AGO, OR WHATEVER THE CASE MAY BE, IS THERE'S
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:31.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BEEN SO MANY DISCOVERIES ABOUT METHODOLOGY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:35.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND WHICH IS SUPERIOR AND WHICH CAN DO\NTHINGS THAT THE OTHER CAN'T.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:37.35,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND I'M NOT GOING TO GET INTO ALL THAT RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:40.06,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, WHICH IS KIND OF, YOU KNOW, WE'RE\NOPENING THE DOOR TO THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.22,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S GOING TO BE THE FUN STUFF WE'RE GOING\NTO BE ABLE TO TALK ABOUT, EXACTLY, THIS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,EPISODE AND ALL THESE FUTURE EPISODES TO\NCOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:52.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M JUST EXCITED TO BE ABLE TO DO THIS WITH\NYOU. STRAIGHT FROM THE HART, OKAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:55.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,MY LAST NAME IS HART, SO THERE YOU GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND I AM GOING TO GIVE IT TO YOU STRAIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.48,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE OTHER PART OF THAT TITLE IS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:05.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,STRAIGHT FROM THE HART BECAUSE HVAC CLEANING\NSHOULD BE A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND YOU KNOW, THAT HAS A COUPLE OF PLAYS TO\NIT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.40,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT SHOULD BE A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE, MEANING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S THE METHOD THAT WE'RE GOING TO\NDISCUSS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:16.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IS POSITIVE AIR DUCT CLEANING AS OPPOSED TO\NNEGATIVE AIR DUCT CLEANING.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND YOU KNOW, IT SHOULD BE POSITIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT SHOULD BE A FUN THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:23.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT SHOULD BE A JOY FOR EVERYBODY DOING IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.75,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OUR CUSTOMERS, WHEN WE DO DUCT CLEANING FOR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,PEOPLE, MAN, WE HAVE SO MANY FIVE-STAR\NREVIEWS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:32.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,PEOPLE TYPE IN, "MY SON'S ASTHMA IS ALL BUT\NGONE."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,"WE'RE BREATHING BETTER."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,"I'M NOT DUSTING EVERY SINGLE DAY."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO IT IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:38.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S JUST A POSITIVE THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:43.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I LIKE HOW YOU SAY OUR CUSTOMERS BECAUSE\NRAMAIR SELLS EQUIPMENT TO PROFESSIONAL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.77,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,REMEDIATORS WHO THEN PERFORM SERVICE FOR\NCUSTOMERS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.58,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND YOU THINK IN THE MIND OF YOUR CUSTOMERS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.38,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,FOR THE END CUSTOMER, HOW YOU MAKE THEIR\NLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:54.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BETTER. HOW DO YOU MAKE THEIR LIFE A MORE\NPOSITIVE EXPERIENCE, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.82,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, IT'S FUNNY YOU WOULD SAY THAT BECAUSE,\NYES, I DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:03.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE REASON I DO IS BECAUSE I AM ONE OF\NOUR CUSTOMERS ALSO, OKAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S LIKE THE HAIR CLUB FOR MEN [HAIRCLUB].
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I DON'T JUST OWN THE COMPANY.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M ALSO A CLIENT, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:12.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE DON'T JUST DESIGN AND MANUFACTURE\NGROUNDBREAKING AIR DUCT CLEANING EQUIPMENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:16.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE USE IT EVERY SINGLE DAY OUT IN THE FIELD\NAND WE ARE SO BUSY, ESPECIALLY RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.89,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M OPERATING IN THE FIELD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.06,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IN FACT, YESTERDAY I SPOKE WITH YOU ON THE\NPHONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:22.34,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I HAD TO GET GOING BECAUSE I WAS IN THE\NMIDDLE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OF A FORENSIC RESTORATION JOB WHERE WE WERE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:34.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DOING A MOLD REMEDIATION JOB AND SO, YEAH,\NWE ARE USING THE STUFF EVERY SINGLE DAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YEAH, THAT'S GREAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO LET'S TALK ABOUT SOME OF THE BENEFITS TO\NEND USERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO LET'S TALK ABOUT THE FOUR.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:44.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE TALKED ABOUT FOUR KEY BENEFITS OF THE\NPOSITIVE AIR DUCT CLEANING METHOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:47.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE FIRST ONE IS A ONE-PERSON JOB.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN DO ONE PERSON, CAN DO THE WHOLE JOB.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,TALK ABOUT THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:54.97,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, IN OUR COMPANY, WE SEND EACH VAN AND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:05:00.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,TEAM OUT. AND I PUT TEAM LIKE THAT BECAUSE\NIT IS ONE PERSON.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:05.34,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S ONE-PERSON ROUTES AND THEY DO TWO\NHOUSES PER DAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,GET BACK USUALLY BETWEEN FOUR OR FIVE IN THE\NAFTERNOON.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO THERE YOU GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:11.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S AMAZING.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, YOU SAVE SO MUCH ON LABOR AND YOU\NCAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:17.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ACTUALLY MAKE QUITE A BIT OF PROFIT THEN ON\NA JOB, PER JOB.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, YOU CAN SEND TWO OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ANY MORE THAN THAT, IT'S GETTING BE QUITE A\NFEW.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:25.82,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, YOU CAN HAVE A HELPER GO, YOU KNOW,\NIT'S A HAND STUFF AND MAYBE BE DOING SOME
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND IT DOES GO VERY, VERY SMOOTHLY WITH TWO\NPEOPLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.98,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M NOT KNOCKING THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.92,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S JUST THAT IT WORKS SO WELL WITH ONE IS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:35.10,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DESIGNED AROUND ONE IF YOU WANT TO HAVE A\NSECOND.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.10,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU KNOW, IT'S NICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO ONE PERSON-JOBS. THE SECOND THING IS THAT\NIT'S NONINVASIVE, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,TALK ABOUT THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:45.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S A NONINVASIVE APPROACH TO AIR DUCT\NCLEANING.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NONINVASIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.72,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, IN THIS PARTICULAR CASE, THEY WAY WE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.58,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ARE USING THAT TERM, WE ARE NOT CUTTING A\NBIG
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:58.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HOLE INTO THE HVAC SYSTEM IN ORDER TO HOOK\NEQUIPMENT UP TO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:03.82,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND IN THE TRADITIONAL WAY THAT THE DUCTS\NARE CLEANED, THAT'S WHAT TAKES PLACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.94,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU PULL UP WITH EITHER A TRUCK MOUNTED OR A
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:11.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,PORTABLE MACHINE THAT SUCKS AT LARGE\NQUANTITIES OF AIR.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.77,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU CUT INTO THE DUCT SYSTEM AND YOU EXTRACT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:17.10,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE AIR FROM THE DUCTS, CREATING NEGATIVE\NPRESSURE INSIDE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.40,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S WHY IT'S CALLED NEGATIVE AIR DUCT\NCLEANING,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,CREATING NEGATIVE PRESSURE INSIDE THOSE\NDUCTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:25.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND WE'RE GOING TO GET A LOT INTO THAT LATER\NIN THIS AND FUTURE EPISODES AS WELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.98,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BUT ,OURS IS NONINVASIVE BECAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:34.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE'RE NOT BRINGING THAT MASS AIR MOVER TO\NTHE JOB SITE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.58,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT MASS AIR MOVER IS ALREADY THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU KNOW, FOR SUCCESSFUL HVAC CLEANING, YOU\NNEED THREE ELEMENTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:43.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU NEED MASS AIR MOVEMENT, AGITATION, AND\NVACUUM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:48.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, THE MASS AIR MOVEMENT, WHICH IS, AS I\NMENTIONED, THE MACHINE THAT THEY BRING UP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:52.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND CUT INTO THE DUCTS, I SAID THAT OURS IS\NALREADY THERE AND DELIVERED.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:57.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S THE AIR HANDLER, THE FURNACE FAN, THE\NAIR HANDLER FAN ITSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:02.10,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND IT'S NOT ONLY DELIVERED TO THE JOB SITE,\NIT'S ALREADY HOOKED UP TO THE DUCTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S READY TO GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:08.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND EVEN BETTER YET, WE LEAVE IT AT THE JOB\NSITE WHEN WE'RE DONE WE JUST LEAVE IT HOOKED UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:12.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO WE DON'T HAVE TO TAKE IT BACK, CLEAN IT\NOUT, MAINTAIN AND ALL THAT KIND OF STUFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT DID THE JOB FOR US.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:18.98,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SECONDLY, IN REGARD TO THAT, IT'S THE RIGHT\NAMOUNT OF AIR FLOW FOR THE JOB WE'RE DOING.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.21,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, IF WE'RE DOING A RESIDENTIAL HOME, SAY\NA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,2500 SQUARE FOOT HOUSE, WE HAVE AN AIR MOVER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.08,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT IS MOVING THAT AIR AT THE CORRECT\NAMOUNT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OF SPEED FOR THAT PARTICULAR DUCT SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOT TOO MUCH, NOT TOO LITTLE, IT'S JUST\NRIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:33.07,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, IF WE GET INTO A COMMERCIAL JOB, AND MY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,PERSONAL HVAC CLEANING COMPANY HAS DONE\NEIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,CASINOS IN THE LAST FEW YEARS, THESE ARE\NHUGE,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:42.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HUGE HUNDREDS OF THOUSANDS OF SQUARE FEET OF\NSPACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:45.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THEY DON'T JUST HAVE LITTLE RESIDENTIAL AIR\NHANDLERS IN THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:49.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THEY HAVE AIR HANDLERS ON THE ROOFTOP THAT\NARE THE SIZE OF SHIPPING CONTAINERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.82,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU WALK INTO THESE THINGS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:55.01,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE NOT, THEY'RE NOT MOVING 2000, 5000,\NEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:58.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,15000 CFM OF AIR MOVEMENT, WHICH IS\NCONSIDERED
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,A LOT FOR NEGATIVE AIR MACHINE TO MOVE 15000\NCFM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S A LOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.20,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THESE THINGS ARE PUSHING 60000. 60000 CFM OF\NAIR.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:09.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO WHAT CAN YOU BRING THAT THEY DON'T\NALREADY HAVE, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DRIVE A DUCT\NTRUCK INTO THE MIDDLE OF A CASINO?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN'T DO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:16.17,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO USE THE\NPORTABLES, AND THAT'S
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,JUST, OH MY GOD, IT'S GOING TO TAKE FOREVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.12,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE DID A CASINO A COUPLE OF YEARS AGO DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IN CALIFORNIA, WHERE THEY HAD GOTTEN A QUOTE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:27.98,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,FROM ANOTHER COMPANY THAT WAS GOING TO\NCHARGE, I'LL JUST GO AHEAD AND TELL YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THIS IS CALLED STRAIGHT FROM THE HART,\NRIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:30.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I LOVE IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M GOING TO SHOOT IT STRAIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:34.40,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE'RE GOING TO, RIGHT, THEY WERE GOING TO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:38.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,CHARGE $750,000 TO SPEND THREE MONTHS TO GO\NIN AND CLEAN THESE DUCTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:44.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S INVASIVE INTO A CASINO WHEN YOU HAVE\NPEOPLE WHO, BY THE WAY, ARE ALSO DRINKING,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.64,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND WALKING AROUND IN THIS PLACE FOR YOU TO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.94,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BE RUNNING YOUR SHOW THERE FOR THREE MONTHS,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:50.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SECTIONING OFF AREAS AND ALL THAT KIND OF\NSTUFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THEY WANT IT DONE QUICKLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:55.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THEY WANT IT DONE WELL, BUT THEY ALSO WANTED\NDONE EFFICIENTLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:09:01.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE DID THAT JOB IN 10 DAYS. GRANTED WE DID\NIT FOR HALF AS MUCH, BUT I'D RATHER MAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:04.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,$300K AND SOME IN 10 DAYS THAN $750K IN\NTHREE MONTHS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:05.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OPPORTUNITY COSTS. BECAUSE THEN YOU GO ON\NAND DO SOMETHING ELSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ABSOLUTELY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ABSOLUTELY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S ACTUALLY HIGHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S CONSIDERABLY HIGHER REVENUE GENERATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:16.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO IT'S A VERY, IT'S A GREAT SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:19.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ONE PERSON JOB, IT'S A MINIMALLY INVASIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.32,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ALSO, YOU DON'T NEED NOT TO HAVE THE\NCOMMERCIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:25.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,STUFF, BUT FOR THE RESIDENTIAL, YOU DON'T\NNEED AN HVAC LICENSE, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:31.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, YOU HAVE A PATENT ON THIS SANIJET\NDECONTAMINATION APPLICATION SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:37.76,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE DECONTAMINATION SYSTEM, THE SANIJET, IS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:41.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,PROBABLY MY FAVORITE ASPECT TO THE WHOLE\NTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:45.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE REASON BEING IS THERE ARE OTHER WAYS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:49.34,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OF CLEANING DUCTS THAN THE POSITIVE AIR\NMETHOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.64,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ARE THEY GOOD FOR THE DUCTS?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:51.94,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DO THEY DO AS GOOD OF A JOB?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:57.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ONCE AGAIN, WE'RE GOING TO GET INTO THAT IN\NFUTURE EPISODES.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:00.44,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BUT IN ORDER TO APPLY A DECONTAMINANT TO THE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.58,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,INSIDE OF A DUCT SYSTEM, IN THE EVENT OF A
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,RESTORATION JOB, WHETHER IT BE A SMOKE,\NCRIME
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:08.38,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SCENE, UNATTENDED DEATH, HOMICIDE, SUICIDE,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.91,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ILLICIT DRUG, MOLD, WHATEVER WE'RE GOING
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,TO BE APPLYING TO THOSE SURFACES, THE INSIDE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OF THE DUCT WALLS, THERE'S TWO GOLDEN RULES
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.58,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IN THE RESTORATION INDUSTRY THAT EVERYBODY\NIN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.23,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE RESTORATION INDUSTRY IS FAMILIAR WITH,\NAND THAT IS:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU NEED TO COAT THE SURFACE COMPLETELY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:28.34,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND HAS A DWELL FOR A CERTAIN AMOUNT OF\NTIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.57,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE TRADITIONAL WAY OF APPLYING A
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DECONTAMINANT TO THE INSIDE OF AN HVAC\NSYSTEM, AND
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.36,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I USE THE TERM DECONTAMINATE, RATHER THAN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:39.34,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DISINFECTANT, BECAUSE YOU USE A DISINFECTANT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.49,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IF IT'S A PATHOGEN, WHATEVER THE CASE MAY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:47.06,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BE, ILLICIT DRUG, YOU'RE NOT KILLING\NANYTHING BECAUSE THERE'S NOTHING LIVING.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:50.10,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO IT'S A CHEMICAL NEUTRALIZER IN THAT\NPARTICULAR CASE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:53.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO I USE THE WORD DECONTAMINATE TO COVER\NBOTH DISINFECTANT AND CHEMICAL NEUTRALIZER.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:56.94,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO YOU CAN HEAR ME USING THAT TERM A LOT,\NDECONTAMINATE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.28,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW IF YOU'RE GOING TO APPLY THAT TO THE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,INSIDE OF A DUCT SYSTEM, THE WAY IT'S BEEN\NDONE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.43,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,TRADITIONALLY FOR DECADES IS FOGGING, YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:06.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ALWAYS HEAR ABOUT THEM, AND A FOG THE DUCTS,\NOKAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.34,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE WAY THAT'S DONE IS TO PUT THE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DECONTAMINATE LIQUID INTO A FOGGING MACHINE,\NAND
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.73,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THEN YOU TURN ON THE AIR HANDLER OF THE DUCT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.38,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SYSTEM, GO TO THE RETURN DUCT, AND BLAST\NTHAT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,FOG INTO THE RETURN DUCT WITH THE AIR\NHANDLER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:22.10,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,FAN MOVING, WHICH CARRIES IT THROUGH THE\NDUCT SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.61,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND AT FIRST THAT SOUNDS GREAT, IT SOUNDS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,LIKE IT WORKS, IT CARRIES IT THROUGH THE\NDUCT SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:29.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BUT LET'S EXAMINE THAT PREPOSITION FOR A\NMOMENT, THROUGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:34.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT APPLIES IT THROUGH THE DUCT SYSTEM, NOT\NTO, NOT ON, OKAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.98,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO HOW DOES THAT LOOK?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND I KNOW THIS, BECAUSE I'VE BEEN, I'VE\NBEEN DOING THIS FOR OVER 30 YEARS.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'VE HAD MY HVAC CLEANING COMPANY FOR 28\NYEARS.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:44.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,POSITIVE AIR DUCT CLEANING HAS EXISTED FOR\N18.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:46.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO WHAT DID I DO FOR THE PREVIOUS 10, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OKAY, I WAS THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I WAS DOING IT, ALL RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO YOU GO TO THE RETURN, YOU FOG THE\NDECONTAMINATE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:55.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,INTO THERE, IT CARRIES IT THROUGH THE DUCT,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:59.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND YOU WATCH THOSE SUPPLY DUCTS WHERE THE\NAIR COMES OUT, THOSE REGISTERS, AND YOU CAN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.37,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SEE THE FOG START TO POUR OUT OF THOSE,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,MEANING IT'S NOW GOING THROUGH THE DUCT\NSYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:07.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHAT HAPPENS IS THE PERSON APPLYING IT THEN\NSHUTS THE FOG OFF, OKAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:10.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE'RE NOW FOGGING THE INSIDE OF THE SPACE,\NI'VE DONE THE FOGGING.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.67,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE THING IS, IF YOU SHUT OFF THE FOGGER AT\NTHAT POINT,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:17.22,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU HAVEN'T EVEN BEGUN TO COAT THE INSIDE OF\NTHOSE DUCTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:19.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE ONLY WAY YOU WILL HAVE COATED THE INSIDE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OF THOSE DUCTS, IF YOU KEEP FOGGING TO THE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.29,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,POINT, THAT ALL THAT FOG COMES OUT OF THOSE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.70,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,REGISTERS, YOU WANT TO BE ABLE TO SEE\NTHROUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.10,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE ROOM, YOU WANT TO SEE YOUR HAND IN FRONT
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OF THE FACE, YOU WOULD HAVE FILLED THE\NINTERIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OF THE SPACE, YOU GOT DECONTAMINATE ALL OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.98,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,EVERY SURFACE, IT'S ON THE DUCT SURFACES,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.63,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BUT IT'S ALSO ON THE WALLS, THE CEILING, THE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,FLOOR, THE WINDOWS, ALL THE CONTENTS WITHIN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:45.06,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT STRUCTURE, AND NOBODY DOES THAT, NOBODY\NWOULD DO THAT IN THEIR RIGHT MIND.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO THEY SHUT IT OFF EARLY, AND NOTHING EVER\NGETS DONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:55.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, THE SANIJET, WHICH IS THE PATENTED\NSYSTEM THAT WE DESIGNED ABOUT 15 YEARS AGO,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.01,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE TURN THE HVAC SYSTEM OFF, SO THE AIR IS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.82,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOT GOING THROUGH THE SYSTEM, WE HAVE\NTHROUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.07,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,A COMPRESSED CANISTER, WE FILLED OUR LIQUID\NAS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,A LONG HOSE, AT THE END OF WHICH IS A\NDISPERSION
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:14.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BALL, WE DEPRESS THE LEVER, IT FOGS IT OUT\NOF THAT BALL, AND SPRAYS IT DIRECTLY TO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:17.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE DUCT WALLS AS WE SLOWLY RETRACT THAT\NHOSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.65,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO NOW IT GIVES US COMPLETE CONTROL OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,APPLYING THAT DECONTAMINANT TO THOSE DUCT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WALLS, AND NONE OF IT ENTERS THE LIVING\NSPACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:30.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO YEAH, IT PUTS EXACTLY WHAT YOU WANT,\NWHERE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:34.34,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU WANT IT, AND IT DOESN'T PUT IT WHERE YOU\NDON'T WANT IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.51,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE NOT GOING TO GET THE FOG ALL OVER THE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HOUSE, AND YOU'RE GETTING MORE DISINFECTANT\NINSIDE THE ROOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:42.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE GOING TO GET EXACTLY AS MUCH AS YOU\NWANT WHERE YOU WANT IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S GREAT. THAT'S TERRIFIC. WELL, GREAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.14,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THANK YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THIS IS GOING TO BE A LOT OF FUN, AND WE'RE\NGOING TO BE TALKING TO CUSTOMERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:55.06,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU'VE GOT A BUNCH OF PEOPLE LINED UP, AND\NWE'LL BE HEARING FROM THEIR PERSPECTIVE ON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:58.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHAT IT'S LIKE TO HAVE RAMAIR EQUIPMENT, AND\NHOW THEY CAN BE SUCCESSFUL OPERATING
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:04.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,A BUSINESS, TO HAVE A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE,\NAND GIVE PEOPLE A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.85,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE GOT SOME REALLY GREAT GUESTS LINED UP ON
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:10.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ABSOLUTELY STOKED, ESPECIALLY OUR FIRST ONE,\NBOB JORDAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:14.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HE'S A FORMER AEROSPACE ENGINEER THAT GOT\NINTO RESTORATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HE NOW OWNS A PUROCLEAN FRANCHISE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:21.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HE'S WRITTEN A BOOK ON DITIGATION, AND HE'S\NGOING TO BE OUR FIRST GUEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.85,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE HAVE A GENTLEMAN WHO IS PARAMOUNT IN THE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:30.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,MANUFACTURING OF FLEX DUCTING, SO HE KNOWS\NTHE MANUFACTURING OF IT VERY WELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:36.06,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE HAVE SOME OTHER RESTORERS, AS WELL AS\NUSERS OF DIFFERENT EQUIPMENT OUT THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S GOING TO BE A REAL, REAL FUN TRIP WE'RE\NGOING TO TAKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:39.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, THAT'S GOING TO BE GREAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I LOOK FORWARD TO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE'LL TALK NEXT WEEK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:47.18,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,[MUSIC PLAYING]
